description: Multiply Your Style Fashion-Forward. Keep your iPod safe and secure in a case that's sure to be noticed. The shell has a textured surface pattern with raised "pebbles" that look great and make it easy to grip. Plus, engineered cutouts show off the metallic brushed or anodized inner plate. Protection that Fits The thin, yet durable material is a stylish way to keep your iPod's surface free of scratches and scuffs, without adding extra bulk.
title: Belkin Emerge 032 Case for Apple iPod Touch 4th Generation (Paparazzi Pink)
